; Regression test for issue #610: Whole transaction is ignored when there's a specific comment (BZ#610)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/610
;
; A comment at column 0 (non-indented) between a transaction header and its
; postings used to silently ignore the whole transaction. Ledger now
; produces an error instead of silently dropping the transaction.

2011-12-13 * Test
; test
    A                     10.00 GBP
    B

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
Error: Unexpected whitespace at beginning of line
end test
